{"word":"H8577 - תַּנִּין - tannîyn - tan-neen' - Dragon","slug":"H8577","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">תַּנִּין</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>tannîyn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tan-neen'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Dragon"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05EA;&#x05BC;&#x05E0;&#x05BC;&#x05D9;&#x05DD;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05EA;&#x05BC;&#x05E0;&#x05BC;&#x05D9;&#x05DF; - tann&#x0131;&#x0302;yn  tann&#x0131;&#x0302;ym</b> - <i>tan-neen', tan-neem'</i><p/>(The second form used in <a href='B:330 29:3'>Eze 29:3</a>); intensive from the same as <a href=\"#/H8565\">H8565</a>; a marine or land <i>monster</i>, that is, <i>sea serpent</i> or <i>jackal: - </i>dragon, sea-monster, serpent, whale."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8565\">H8565</a>, <a href=\"#/H8568\">H8568</a>"}]}